See what's next on your calendar, every time you open the new tab page. A simple, beautiful Chrome extension that helps you keep on top of your day, and jump into your next appointment without going to another website.

Up Next currently only supports the Chrome browser, using a Google account to access your Calendar. All requests are performed locally, on your machine, and are not sent to any third-party services.
